data.description: This stunning property boasts a spacious layout with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1723 square feet of living space. It features an inviting ground pool complete with a slide, as well as a covered hot tub for luxurious relaxation. Modern amenities include a tankless water heater and solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. Remodeled in 2014, the home showcases new flooring throughout, complemented by a contemporary walk-in shower in the master bedroom. Outside, a circular driveway and RV parking provide ample space for vehicles. The backyard is adorned with fruit trees and sheds for additional storage. Appliances such as a refrigerator, washer, dryer, microwave, and gas stovetop are included, along with a double oven, one of which is convection. Central heat and AC, installed in 2017, offer year-round comfort. With its desirable location in Loomis and access to Del Oro School, this property is priced at $668,500, making it an exceptional find for discerning buyers. Seize this opportunity to live in a charming Loomis neighborhood.
